            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41128",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "And how should the array adapter know which language the translation has?\r\nI think that you missed something in your workflow.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-06-21T08:11:11.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-06-21T08:11:11.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41133",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=renepardon",
                        "name": "renepardon",
                        "displayName": "Christoph, Ren\u00e9 Pardon",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hi Ramon,\r\n\r\nthis is probably no bug! You have to assign a language\/locale to the adapter to get it working as expected.\r\nYou can pass the locale as second parameter. Zend_Translate_Adapter will then add your array to the assigned locale.\r\n\r\nbest regards",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=renepardon",
                        "name": "renepardon",
                        "displayName": "Christoph, Ren\u00e9 Pardon",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-06-21T09:56:30.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-06-21T09:56:30.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41135",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ramon",
                        "name": "ramon",
                        "displayName": "Ramon Henrique Ornelas",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thomas\r\n\r\nBefore of the release 1.10.3 this code worked correctly.\r\n{code}\r\nnew Zend_Translate_Adapter_Array(array('message' => 'Foo'));\r\n{code}\r\n\r\n\r\nAfter of the release 1.10.3 was need of change to\r\n{code}\r\nnew Zend_Translate_Adapter_Array(array('content' => array('message' => 'Foo')));\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nSince already Thanks ;).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ramon",
                        "name": "ramon",
                        "displayName": "Ramon Henrique Ornelas",
